**Rules:** 14x14 units, spacing every 18 units (example 19/37/55/73). Never (0,0). Start `position_y: 1`.

**Patterns:** Linear (19,1)→(37,1)→(55,1). Branching: success (37,1), error (37,19). </positioning_system>

